:: a pack of cigarettes {"position":"325,1075","size":"100,100"}
### A pack of cigarettes
You're kind of trying to quit, but man, you could really go for one right now. (if: $cigs > 0)[It looks like you've only got (text: $cigs) left.

You could (link:'light one up now')[($addToInventory:'a pack of cigarettes')($showItem:'report smoking'))].\
](else:)[But you are totally out.]



:: a piece of jade [item] {"position":"200,350","size":"100,100"}
(metadata: 'inventory', 'item')
### A piece of jade
Grandma said it will bring you luck, which hasn't really been working out. You can't remember now how it ended up in your pickup truck. Maybe someday you'll see someone lucky and you can throw it at him.


